---
title: Warming Squash and Lentil Dal with Brown Rice
description: What do you get when you combine squash with lentils, spices and diced tomatoes in a big pot? A delicious dal! Anything that uses one pot is magic in our books. It tastes pretty magical too!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/warming-squash-and-lentil-dal-5c3aa41b.jpg
